org.eclipse.scada.vi.details.model

Interface ValueSetComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component, ReadableComponent, WriteableComponent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ValueSetComponentImpl

    public interface ValueSetComponent
extends WriteableComponent
    A representation of the model object 'Value Set Component'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Value Descriptor
    • Set Descriptor
    • Reset Descriptor

    See Also:
    DetailViewPackage.getValueSetComponent()
